---
title: "AI Index Settings — Cuento Docs"
---

      <div class="docs-eyebrow">Admin Panel</div>
      <h1 class="docs-title">AI Index Settings</h1>
      <p class="docs-lead">
        AI Index Settings control which content types are included in the search index for each subforum.
        Each column represents a content type; each row is a subforum. Check a cell to include that
        content type from that subforum in the AI-powered search index.
      </p>

      <div class="docs-screenshot">
        <img src="/assets/screenshots/admin-ai-index-settings.png" alt="AI Index Settings page screenshot" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="docs-h2">Content Types</h2>

      <div class="field-list">

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">characters</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes character sheet topics from this subforum — names, descriptions, and custom template fields.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">episodes</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes episode (in-character) topics from this subforum, including their structured header fields.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">game_posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes individual in-character posts written inside episode topics in this subforum.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">general_posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes posts from general (out-of-character) topics in this subforum.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">lore_posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes posts from lore topics in this subforum.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">wanted_posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Indexes wanted character listings from this subforum.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <h2 class="docs-h2">Saving</h2>
      <p class="docs-p">
        Click <strong>Save</strong> at the bottom of the page to apply all checkbox changes at once.
        The index is updated after saving — newly checked subforums and content types will be
        included in subsequent search queries.
      </p>
